Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.37,0:24:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是藏在某個地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.21,0:24:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不在嗎
